      "message": "minijail_sys::rlim_t is defined to be u64 in minijail-sys/libminijail.rs.\n\nlibc::rlim64_t is defined to be u64 on linux, uclibc, emscripten and fuchsia, but undefined on android, because the C (i.e. Bionic) headers on Android don\u0027t define it.\n\n`struct rlimit64_t` in Bionic (https://cs.android.com/android/platform/superproject/+/master:bionic/libc/kernel/uapi/linux/resource.h;l\u003d50?q\u003drlimit\u0026sq\u003d\u0026ss\u003dandroid%2Fplatform%2Fsuperproject:bionic%2F) uses __u64 for its members directly.",
